	[src/strtofr.c] Continued to review the new error analysis and code.
	Changes:
	  * made the code more SSA-like (avoid a "y += ysize; y -= ysize;");
	  * clarified comments;
	  * use MPFR_LIMB_MSB;
	  * added a FIXME on the error analysis.

