	  perl -pi -e 's/ (\d{4}-)?(2014)(?= Free Software)/
	               " ".($1||"$2-").($2+1)/e' **/*(^/)
	under zsh, reverting the tools/mbench directory (not distributed with
	MPFR). Removed 2014 from the example in the doc/README.dev file.

