2007-07-17  Paul Zimmermann  <Paul.Zimmermann@inria.fr>

	previous bug fix for tiny negative inputs in mpfr_lgamma was incorrect:
	result was NaN, but this was not detected by the tests since mpfr_cmp (y, NaN)
	is always true!

