	Added LIA-2 functions to implement.

2005-05-04  Patrick Pélissier  <patrick.pelissier@gmail.com>

	Add functions mpfr_sech, mpfr_coth and mpfr_csch.

	init2 alloc what is needed, not 2 (more efficient).

