	Back to version 2.0.1, updated documentation.

	Post-release commit.

	Update for mpfr 2.0.1.

	mpfr_cmp_ui_2exp and mpfr_cmp_si_2exp can no longer be called with a NaN.
	Misc bugs fixed.

